f="https://www.thivien.net/Ng%C3%B4-Th%E1%BA%BF-L%C3%A2n/author-ZqTE_3GO97Ws9hNrgzlGIw">Ngô Thế Lân</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%B4ng-B%E1%BA%A3n-thi%E1%BB%81n-s%C6%B0/S%C6%A1n-c%C6%B0-b%C3%A1ch-v%E1%BB%8Bnh-k%E1%BB%B3-093/poem-oDr2hzx4pcxME62HCqwdbg">Sơn cư bách vịnh kỳ 093 - 山居百詠其九十三</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%B4ng-B%E1%BA%A3n-thi%E1%BB%81n-s%C6%B0/author-jnvtlp5PrNS3FoOBBGt7-w">Tông Bản thiền sư</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%B4-Th%E1%BB%A9c/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-ch%C3%A2u/poem-cfhCIz1YtX2OiOxJFolHGg">Trần châu - 陳州</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%B4-Th%E1%BB%A9c/author-ZsPeAEZWTH-jxxg2cYfLgg">Tô Thức</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/B%E1%BA%A1ch-C%C6%B0-D%E1%BB%8B/Tr%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Dng-h%E1%BA%ADn-ca/poem-NNj51-ebZyApj8ndjN6_VQ">Trường hận ca - 長恨歌</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/B%E1%BA%A1ch-C%C6%B0-D%E1%BB%8B/author-GTDxHQP8eUITUxph4otjnA">Bạch Cư Dị</a>)<br></div>	</div>
